    [Ellipse.java] The class represents the ellipse shape, which inherits from the simple shape class.
    GeometryDrawingProgram
    [GeometryDrawingProgram.java] The program allows the user to add shapes, remove shapes, translate shapes and save and load files on to a cartesian plane.
    GeometryDrawingProgram.GeometryScreen
    The class is an inner class of GeometryDrawingProgram that creates the screen that the shapes are drawn in.
    GeometryDrawingProgram.GeometryScreen.GraphicsPanel
    The class is an inner class of GeometryScreen that draws the shapes and the grid to the screen.
    Grid
    [Grid.java] The class represents the cartesian plane that encompasses all of the shapes on the screen.

    [Parallelogram.java] The class represents the parallelogram shape, which inherits from the complex shape class.

    [Rectangle.java] The class represents the rectangle shape, which inherits from the simple shape class.
